{
  "stem": "26888.1",
  "chunk_idx": 7,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 7.5,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "Um-- what do you call it, a head surgeon, maybe?",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And how were they related to you?",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "It's, uh, my mother-- uh, my mother's, um, uncle.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "That's my grandfather's brother.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] And, uh, they were very orthodox, uh, family.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, it was very strict.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "We, uh, [PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] have to pray, you know, the girls.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Well, I didn't go to a parochial school, but we had somebody who was coming in, you know, and teach.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "That's because they didn't really have a girl's-- they didn't have a orthodox school.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "They didn't have, so, uh-- but, uh-- I still remain-- I'm not that orthodox like my mother, but my home, it's-- my children are orthodox.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Peggy, children, and, uh-- I remain like that because I come up from home with it.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And, uh-- [PAUSE] Well, you see-- you say, well, how could you live so much through and what happened this and this.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "But when it comes to life, you go back what you saw at home.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "I mean, not everybody, but I did.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "My younger sister-- my sister who had died, was very, very orthodox.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "She lived in Bnei Brak.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "She left $1 million for the yeshivas.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "She built-- she built a school for 300 children, a yeshiva.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "She built-- there is the rabbi in Bnei Brak.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "She built for him a place where he has-- he-- the people when they're coming, they're coming in that place, and the name is there.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "She built also for people who can't afford, they want to make a wedding and bar mitzvahs and things like that.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "She built that too, but she never had children.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "That was [INAUDIBLE].",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "My favorite holiday was Pesach.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 53,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "[INAUDIBLE] I got some nice things always.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 53,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "[LAUGHS] New things.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 53,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Yeah.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 53,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "You had a dress.",
      "word_count": 4
    }
  ],
